A vintage 1970s technical illustration style scene showing two translucent glass boxes floating side by side, one containing a glowing orange phoenix-like flame creature, the other housing a sleek metallic penguin with circuit patterns on its feathers. Between them, a brass toggle switch on an ornate mechanical control panel, with gears and steam pipes connecting the two containers. The background is aged parchment with faded blueprint grid lines. Warm sepia tones dominate with pops of electric blue and amber, creating a retrofuturistic atmosphere of competing technologies sharing the same space through elegant mechanical arbitration.
